c: 2
v: 214
t: "Or (have) you thought/supposed that you enter the Paradise and (the) example of those who past/expired from before you (E) did not come to you, the misery/hardship and the calamity touched them, and they were shaken until the messenger and those who believed with him say: \"When (is) God`s victory/aid?\" Is it not (that) God`s victory/aid (is) near/close"